Package ru.introguzzle.parsers.common.io.watch

Interface Report

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<Report>
All Known Implementing Classes:
InspectingFileWatcher.AbstractReport, InspectingFileWatcher.CreateReport, InspectingFileWatcher.DeleteReport, InspectingFileWatcher.ModifyReport
public interface Report extends Iterable<Report>
The Report interface represents a file system event report generated by the FileWatcher. It provides information about the type of event, the file path, timestamp, and a reference to the previous report.
